&ldquo;No. On the Whatsapp&rsquo;s group, the last move there was Hazard&rsquo;s farewell. He said goodbye to the boys and such, since then, we don&rsquo;t know anything else. It&rsquo;s weird. He sent a &lsquo;thank you, I love you guys&rsquo;, and then it showed &lsquo;Eden Hazard left the group&rsquo;. I said damn, he really left.&rdquo;

